Remote Desktop Tips and Tricks
[Original Blog Post](https://blog.codinghorror.com/remote-desktop-tips-and-tricks/)

---

Special Remote Desktop Key Combinations:

- `Ctrl + Alt + End`: Send Ctrl+Alt+Del to the remote machine.
- `Alt + Page Up`: Switch between programs on the remote desktop, moving from left to right.
- `Alt + Page Down`: Switch between programs on the remote desktop, moving from right to left.
- `Alt + Insert`: Cycle through the programs in most recently used order.
- `Alt + Home`: Display the Start menu on the remote desktop.
- `Ctrl + Alt + (+/-)`: Adjust the remote desktop display's resolution.

---
In a windowed mode, clikc on the window boarder and select smart sizing for better overall user experience :)


